  uris 's subsequent works included : mila 18 , about the warsaw ghetto uprising ; armageddon : a novel of berlin , a chronicle which ends with the lifting of the berlin blockade in 1949 ; trinity , about irish nationalism and the sequel , redemption , covering the early 20th century and world war i ; qb vii , about the role of a polish doctor in a german concentration camp ; and the haj , set in the history of the middle east .

